# 🛡️ SOI Accessibility Guardian

## Mandatory Text Readability Standards

### WCAG Compliance Requirements
- **Level AA**: Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text
- **Level AAA**: Target 7:1 contrast ratio for optimal readability
- **Large Text**: Minimum 3:1 ratio (18pt+ or 14pt+ bold)
- **Interactive Elements**: Minimum 3:1 for focus indicators

### Pre-Approved Color Combinations

#### ✅ SAFE TEXT COMBINATIONS
```css
/* Primary Text Combinations */
.navy-on-white { color: #1e3a5f; background: #ffffff; } /* 12.6:1 ✅ */
.white-on-navy { color: #ffffff; background: #1e3a5f; } /* 12.6:1 ✅ */
.purple-on-white { color: #8B5C9E; background: #ffffff; } /* 6.2:1 ✅ */
.white-on-purple { color: #ffffff; background: #8B5C9E; } /* 6.2:1 ✅ */

/* Accent Combinations */
.navy-on-light-pink { color: #1e3a5f; background: #f8f4f6; } /* 11.5:1 ✅ */
.navy-on-light-mint { color: #1e3a5f; background: #f4f8f4; } /* 11.2:1 ✅ */
.mint-on-navy { color: #a8c4a2; background: #1e3a5f; } /* 5.1:1 ✅ */
.pink-on-navy { color: #d4a5b8; background: #1e3a5f; } /* 4.8:1 ✅ */
```

#### ⚠️ RESTRICTED COMBINATIONS
```css
/* Use only for decorative elements, never for text */
.pink-on-white { color: #d4a5b8; background: #ffffff; } /* 3.1:1 ⚠️ */
.mint-on-white { color: #a8c4a2; background: #ffffff; } /* 2.8:1 ❌ */
.light-purple { color: #b88cc8; } /* ❌ Never use for text */
```

## Component-Specific Accessibility Rules

### Buttons
```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT Button Implementation
<button className="bg-soi-navy text-white border-2 border-soi-pink hover:bg-soi-navy/90 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-soi-mint focus:ring-offset-2">
  {/* Navy bg + White text = 12.6:1 contrast */}
  Book Appointment
</button>

// ❌ INCORRECT - Poor contrast
<button className="bg-soi-pink text-white">
  {/* Pink bg + White text = 2.4:1 contrast - FAILS */}
</button>
```

