## Emergency Accessibility Fixes

### Quick Contrast Fixes
```css
/* If contrast is too low, use these emergency overrides */
.emergency-high-contrast {
  color: #000000 !important;
  background: #ffffff !important;
}

.emergency-button-fix {
  background: #1e3a5f !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
  border: 2px solid #ffffff !important;
}
```

### Focus State Emergencies
```css
/* If focus states are invisible */
.emergency-focus {
  outline: 3px solid #a8c4a2 !important;
  outline-offset: 2px !important;
}
```

