## Violation Response Protocol

### Critical Violations (Immediate Fix Required)
- Text contrast below 3:1
- Keyboard navigation broken
- Screen reader cannot access content
- Color-only information conveyance

### Major Violations (Fix within 24 hours)
- Text contrast below 4.5:1
- Missing focus indicators
- Insufficient color differentiation
- Poor semantic markup

### Minor Violations (Fix within 1 week)
- Contrast below 7:1 (AAA level)
- Minor screen reader improvements
- Enhanced keyboard shortcuts
- Better color coding alternatives